{"tid":1064982,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣面對廢老無得升同事","createTime":"2019-03-17T03:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T05:18:00.000Z","uid":8043,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4c5b6f0935dc695db269b034c160a5188d34aafe","tid":1064982,"uid":8043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"本身fg 入公司已經高級過佢，但<br />\n一開始佢懶係地頭蟲，教果樣又教另一樣，<br />\n<br />\n做耐左，發現原來無料扮4條，做野做到on99咁，<br />\n<br />\n而家做耐左，我仲升左兩級，變左高佢幾級，<br />\n<br />\n而家feel 到，佢地有意無意中傷我，例如，單單鍋野都同人講話係同我有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後又係咁講，話我係到做無前途，無貢獻<br />\n<br />\n我一直都會敷衍回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為如果我照直講，我驚會太mean  ，同太過招搖 <br />\n<br />\n心入面係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你成4兜野 ，仲做緊<br />\n最低級咋，係公司成567年都無升過，又成屋仔女，你玩完㗎啦<br />\n我就黎又升啦，on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心想請教一下有冇其他更好處理方法？"},{"pid":"554faeae20e9331adfc6ad493588c4ec187f0d75","tid":1064982,"uid":228143,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:08:06.000Z","msg":"大家都係奴隸者....."},{"pid":"940e91877878578040b1e9b4707e6faf11e26fdc","tid":1064982,"uid":68851,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"暗串佢囉 係冇得直接屌㗎啦<br />\n你高級過佢哋 你太認真屌顯得好冇風度<br />\n同埋無論高低職位 收買人心同戴假面具都必要"},{"pid":"0ec35d9a6e143a1ab90175302916b209f46855c8","tid":1064982,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"554faeae20e9331adfc6ad493588c4ec187f0d75","tid":1064982,"uid":228143,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:08:06.000Z","msg":"大家都係奴隸者....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:15:24.000Z","msg":"係 咁應該點"},{"pid":"c9b1d3659fd0bd922d33d386fd20ec0d5ec19a72","tid":1064982,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:17:14.000Z","msg":"1. 有炒人機制就直接威脅<br />\n2. 鼓勵佢重執正軌<br />\n3. 鼓勵佢轉工"},{"pid":"d9f0ec0ed26cd9d5fa1134fe